{"tid":1839231,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史討論：依家好似明朝末年？","createTime":"2020-01-24T10:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T10:30:09.000Z","uid":228441,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8bb4a5068b4952342b00cdb7eb2914222440aa59","tid":1839231,"uid":228441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:22:08.000Z","msg":"雜種就好似崇禎咁，成日以為自己好醒，係畀臣子搞到亡國，其實就係「性多疑而任察，好剛而尚氣。任察則苛刻寡恩，尚氣則急遽失措」。即係話無料又生性多疑，刻薄寡恩（同條撚樣一樣），但永遠唔會覺得責任係自己。<br />\n<br />\n依家就好似明末咁，天災人禍齊齊黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">外患</span></span><br />\n明：女真人<br />\n支共：美俄<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天災</span></span><br />\n明：崇禎六年，山西出現瘟疫。崇禎「七年八年，興縣盜賊殺傷人民，歲饉日甚。天行瘟疫，朝發夕死。至一夜之內，百姓驚逃，城為之空」。<br />\n<br />\n崇禎十六年二月，北京大疫，病名叫「疙瘩病」，「大疫，人鬼錯雜。薄暮人屏不行。貿易者多得紙錢，置水投之，有聲則錢，無聲則紙。甚至白日成陣，牆上及屋脊行走，揶揄居人。每夜則痛哭咆哮，聞有聲而逐有影」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支共：唔使講，豬瘟、肺炎咩柒都有<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人禍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n明：崇禎生性多疑殺袁崇煥、間接累死孫傳庭，重用宦官，瘋狂「加派」收遼餉<br />\n<br />\n支共：貪官當道，搞民企cap水，社保沒收，強行收地<br />\n<br />\n差最後一步......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幾時有流寇出現？希望快d上煤山上吊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab2c9c23c6136f19494dc1c04830545df6f97cb","tid":1839231,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:24:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"3b44cf69e8ab7495bd3f56ec4b512abfae604d2c","tid":1839231,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:26:30.000Z","msg":"老歪脖子樹 is watching 習"},{"pid":"3df9e7c305dfcf66877fb80783acbde649a8ff0a","tid":1839231,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"其實古代疫症長期都有，個問題係你救災、處理方法，人為嘅因素做得好唔好、夠唔夠，朝末成日貪腐，行政力下降，所以特別on9"},{"pid":"86c4516657901e47c8d5f0c852cd19c4c80dc69a","tid":1839231,"uid":299255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:55:42.000Z","msg":"香港個外患咪就係支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04999d0ca396f3c9397b5938c8a2acdfecc62dd4","tid":1839231,"uid":228441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86c4516657901e47c8d5f0c852cd19c4c80dc69a","tid":1839231,"uid":299255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:55:42.000Z","msg":"香港個外患咪就係支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:36:01.000Z","msg":"蛔蛔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c678929d34823a88435622785c47a0400e89f25","tid":1839231,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:42:43.000Z","msg":"等緊小冰河時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3946667e8f2e51576cf910649beb3200ea5b1f","tid":1839231,"uid":143909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:47:46.000Z","msg":"五德終始說又可以拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69a7288a119ff3655900d71fa66f2ba6fd1278b","tid":1839231,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:09:03.000Z","msg":"而家似天降十災的前奏"},{"pid":"e882d12ab8fea125e367d9c262f032b41a1a4242","tid":1839231,"uid":228441,"like":0,"dislike":0